<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="initial-scale=1, minimum-scale=1, width=device-width">
  <link rel="icon" href="/images/me.ico" type="image/meicon">
  <title>Esqueceu a Senha</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 50px;
      background-color: #f2f2f2;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 48px;
      color: #404040;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #606060;
    }

    a, .btn-submit {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      font-size: 16px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #ffffff;
      background-color: #ffd900;
      border-radius: 4px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }

    .btn-submit {
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    a:hover, .btn-submit:hover {
      background-color: #e1c051;
    }

    input[type="email"] {
      padding: 10px;
      font-size: 16px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      width: 300px;
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 50px;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Esqueceu a Senha?</h1>
  <p>Insira seu e-mail abaixo para receber um link de redefinição de senha.</p>
  
  <form action="/reset-password" method="post">
    <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Seu e-mail" required>
    <br>
    <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">Enviar Link</button>
  </form>

  <a href="/">Voltar para a página inicial</a>

  <footer>
    <div class="contact">
      <h3>Contact Us</h3>
      <p>Email: contact@me.finance.com</p>
      <p>Phone: +1 (123) 456-7890</p>
    </div>
    <div class="social">
      <h3>Follow Us</h3>
      <p>Twitter: @MEFinance</p>
      <p>LinkedIn: ME.Finance</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
